text: Tunisian Canadians () are Canadians of Tunisian descent or Tunisians who have Canadian citizenship. Most Tunisian Canadians speak Arabic, French or English. According to the 2016 Census there were 25,645 Canadians who claimed Tunisian ancestry. ==See also== * Arab Canadians * Tunisian Americans == References == == External links == * Category:Arab Canadian Category:Tunisian emigrants to Canada Canadian Category:African Canadian
